@startuml
title UC-06. Посмотреть историю проверок

actor "Пользователь / руководитель" as User
participant "Monitoring API" as API
participant "Result & SLA Module" as ResultSLA
database "Monitoring DB" as DB

User -> API: GET /api/v1/services/{serviceId}/checks?dateFrom&dateTo
API -> ResultSLA: getCheckHistory(serviceId, filters)

ResultSLA -> DB: SELECT check_result\nWHERE service_id = serviceId\nAND checked_at BETWEEN dateFrom AND dateTo
DB --> ResultSLA: check_result list

ResultSLA -> ResultSLA: map to response DTO
ResultSLA --> API: check history
API --> User: 200 OK + check results

@enduml